data.description: A cozy shaded flagstone patio within a fenced back yard is your special place to relax and enjoy Hole #14 at Sun City's White Wing Golf Course! This charming Cambridge plan boasts such nice views from the 4-Seasons Room, Great Room, Kitchen and Primary Bedroom. As part of the open floor plan, the Kitchen with its pretty granite countertops, travertine tile backsplash and stainless appliances is a part of the Great Room and 4-Seasons Room, allowing the cook to enjoy the views out back too! Built with 3 bedrooms/2 baths, one of the two guest bedrooms can easily serve as the study/home office. Great neighbors already in place! Come live your best life in Sun City Texas!
